/Yui_Horie", "name": "Horie, Yui", "language": "Japanese"}, {"image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/voiceactors/2/41312v.jpg", "link": "/people/603/Shannon_Emerick", "name": "Emerick, Shannon", "language": "English"}, {"image": "https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/voiceactors/2/15759v.jpg", "link": "/people/14819/Seung_jun_Kim", "name": "Kim, Seung jun", "language": "Korean"}]}